txt.en: Coffers can be found at Amon Fuin in Parth Daenath.\n\nYou should search the coffers for supplies.
Store the supplies in a chest at Echad-in-Edhil
Coffers can be found at Amon Fuin in Parth Daenath.\n\nYou should search the coffers for supplies.
You deposit the supplies you found into the chest at Echad-in-Edhil. It is your hope that these provisions will be of some use to the war effort of the Great Alliance.
The fortress of Amon Fuin houses the Mordorrim, a cult of evil Men who worship Sauron. The fortress may contain supplies that could be useful for the war effort.
The supplies that you have found should be brought back to Echad-in-Edhil and stored in a chest.
